---
title: Seared Beef Noodles with Broccoli and Carrots
description: Forget the sticky, greasy take away noodle dishes you’ve tried in the past and welcome these noodles into your life! This dish is a healthier option but tastes just as authentic. It is best enjoyed by finding yourself some chopsticks and a deep bowl – get comfy and get slurpin’.
